Package: ClinicalTrialsR
Type: Package
Title: Eases the reporting involved with Clinical Trials Using R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Brian C. Helsel
Maintainer: Brian C. Helsel <bhelsel@kumc.edu>
Description: The purpose of this package is to ease the reporting involved with clinical trials. We are starting with data safety monitoring reports and and then expanding as more use cases evolve.
